    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>带上你的背包进入战场，消灭森林的敌人。 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在《Packmates》中，成为无敌力量的秘密在于你的物品栏。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战略性地安排装备，提升你的构建，与可爱的动物英雄一起征服敌人的浪潮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171540/extras/6e6c6975aa791ed89a59989053354a37.avif?t=1771471354\" width=600 height=115 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171540/extras/d050d748e8aa34192f6691ef2e33841c.poster.avif?t=1771471354\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171540/extras/d050d748e8aa34192f6691ef2e33841c.webm?t=1771471354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171540/extras/d050d748e8aa34192f6691ef2e33841c.mp4?t=1771471354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🎒 优化你的物品栏，提升你的构建。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✨ 构建物品协同效应以增强每次游戏体验。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🤝 在合作模式中协作，分享战利品，并作为一个团队变得更强。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>💪 收集和交易各种库存物品，创造无尽的强大组合！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171540/extras/18ac6519c68c8d5adab913ec192e1adf.avif?t=1771471354\" width=600 height=115 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171540/extras/c4e05f7620536e282b980fef0ab38f27.poster.avif?t=1771471354\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171540/extras/c4e05f7620536e282b980fef0ab38f27.webm?t=1771471354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171540/extras/c4e05f7620536e282b980fef0ab38f27.mp4?t=1771471354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔓 解锁迷人的动物英雄角色，每个角色都有独特的玩法风格来击败boss。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171540/extras/16cd822140eb920224ce138c9988c642.avif?t=1771471354\" width=600 height=115 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171540/extras/2334a75fcccebeec69d3eea5e20c5de0.poster.avif?t=1771471354\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171540/extras/2334a75fcccebeec69d3eea5e20c5de0.webm?t=1771471354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171540/extras/2334a75fcccebeec69d3eea5e20c5de0.mp4?t=1771471354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 <strong>通过每次游戏提高效率，享受通过消灭对手带来的爽快战斗！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🏅 打破记录，积累奖励，完成具有挑战性的目标。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>⚡️ 通过类Rogue进程享受无尽的重玩性和提升的能力。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>勇敢地面对荒野。 成为森林传奇！</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171540/extras/d1462046846cb8fa31516a48d0a0fe6a.poster.avif?t=1771471354\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets